      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We lost so much from our family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The-- if not there, would be in our-- in our section, from Ukraine would be alive today-- 60% people would be alive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because the-- the German came three, four people and the rest was the-- the-- the-- the-- Banderas with the police and everything in the-- in the-- in the forest, where the people, the Jewish people ran out to the forest was killed through the [NON-ENGLISH] and Bandera, the party Bandera.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
